                    <li>MOA and AOA (Pvt Ltd) OR LLP Agreement (LLP) OR Partnership Deed (Partnership Firm) OR Bye-laws (Cooperative)</li>
                    <li>Latest audited financial statements (if entity is more than 1 year old)</li>
                    <li>Founder details - PAN, Aadhaar, address proof, brief professional background of each founder</li>
                    <li>Brief description of the business explaining the innovation, scalable model or Deep Tech research angle</li>
                    <li>Pitch deck (10-15 slides covering problem, solution, traction, business model, market, competition, team, financials)</li>
                    <li>Website URL of the company / mobile app link if applicable</li>
                    <li>Video pitch URL (optional - 1-3 minute video; recommended for cleaner Deep Tech and innovation-heavy applications)</li>
                    <li>Awards / recognitions / accolades won by the company or founders (optional but boosts the application)</li>
                    <li>Patent / trademark / copyright details if any IPR filed</li>
                    <li>Customer testimonials, MoUs, LoIs or sample contracts demonstrating traction (optional)</li>
                    <li>Email and phone number of an authorised representative for application correspondence</li>
                </ul>

